            <pb n="1" facs="#D_000146-021-000-facs001-l001-p001"/>
            <p xml:id="uuid_94addb6d-d902-4a80-a815-1a7368d1aae7" part="N"><lb xml:id="uuid_744fa5fd-e363-4bf5-8fa5-fde3630bf52d"/>Verkündet am 2. März 1931,
                    <lb xml:id="uuid_a809a9bf-1c80-4ce1-89a9-bf1c804ce19d"/>(gez.) <rs type="person" ref="#pmb57472">Hübethal</rs>, Justizangestellter, </p>
            <p xml:id="uuid_c80471cc-c2f2-4bd2-ad48-2cb57366c7f0" part="N"><lb xml:id="uuid_7041f0bc-7cf4-4dd8-81f0-bc7cf44dd821"/>3.0.2007.31/2. </p>
            <p xml:id="uuid_c914e8a4-f247-4046-bbf3-02f8c4bdeb41" part="N"><lb xml:id="uuid_720f55ea-2068-49f1-8f55-ea2068f9f1db"/>In Sachen des
                Schriftstellers <rs type="person" ref="#pmb11988">Karl Kraus</rs>
                <rs type="place" subtype="address" ref="#pmb50496">in Wien III, <lb xml:id="uuid_eb7f0121-b0bb-42ad-bf01-21b0bb92addf"/>Hintere Zollamtsstrasse
                    3</rs>, </p>
            <p xml:id="uuid_f1a6d0cd-4fc6-4132-ab34-a6af3842d7e5" part="N"><lb xml:id="uuid_b98831fc-6a52-426e-8831-fc6a52626e3d"/>Klägers, <lb xml:id="uuid_c24a9c4c-912b-4861-8a9c-4c912bc8613e"/>– Prozeßbevollmächtigter:
                Rechtsanwalt Dr.<rs type="person" ref="#pmb38969">Botho Laserstein</rs> , <rs type="place" subtype="address" ref="#pmb51751">Berlin
                    NO.18, <lb xml:id="uuid_0e28604b-0518-4e35-a860-4b05184e3511"/>Landsbergerallee
                    55</rs>, </p>
            <p xml:id="uuid_b87fbda8-12d7-4d02-95d7-b9cf70eba1a8" part="N"><lb xml:id="uuid_a5e0634e-68b1-4cc1-a063-4e68b1ccc14f"/>gegen den Theaterdirektor
                Ernst Joseph <rs type="person" ref="#pmb37761">Aufricht</rs>, <rs type="place" subtype="address" ref="#pmb56965">Berlin W., <lb xml:id="uuid_14e6735d-bdbb-4895-a673-5dbdbba895f8"/>Landauerstrasse 4</rs>,
                    <lb xml:id="uuid_6773c709-4864-4384-b3c7-0948649384f4"/>Beklagten, </p>
            <p xml:id="uuid_4c159eb3-6750-43ed-8f13-036dc3f9b8f7" part="N"><lb xml:id="uuid_0e56e6ca-1063-4f60-96e6-ca1063df609c"/>wegen 2.753.45 Rmk. </p>
            <p xml:id="uuid_a054be84-c5b2-4445-bb40-b2a4ff982ce8" part="N"><lb xml:id="uuid_890649fd-079d-4557-8649-fd079d455721"/>hat die 3. Zivilkammer des
                    <rs type="institution" ref="#pmb36834">Landgerichts III Berlin</rs> " </p>
            <p xml:id="uuid_c30a62c4-a912-4381-9fad-cae61c4687e5" part="N"><lb xml:id="uuid_cca16c3e-3b5c-471d-a16c-3e3b5c671d80"/>durch den
                Landgerichtsdirektor Dr. <rs type="person" ref="#pmb57474">Püschel</rs>, den
                Landgerichtsrat <lb xml:id="uuid_4d247831-89ca-4b23-a478-3189ca9b23d6"/>Dr. <rs type="person" ref="#pmb57476">Lampson</rs> und den Gerichtsassessor <rs type="person" ref="#pmb57520">Wolff</rs>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="uuid_375183be-bf61-4677-ba79-0afb4c8a84e5" part="N"><lb xml:id="uuid_a2f7e872-aa15-4cfa-b7e8-72aa152cfa7e"/>für Recht erkannt: </p>
            <p xml:id="uuid_6fa3e6f6-17e8-4d8f-9d08-3a47c4d7f375" part="N"><lb xml:id="uuid_6f64e957-1916-4638-a4e9-571916a638dc"/>Der <rs type="person" ref="#pmb37761">Beklagte</rs> wird verurteilt, an den <rs type="person" ref="#pmb11988">Kläger</rs> 2753.45 Rmk. (zwei<lb xml:id="uuid_ec7a8f46-4c6e-49e6-ba8f-464c6e79e68d" break="no"/>tausendsiebenhundertdreiundfünfzig 45 / 100 Reichsmark) zu <lb xml:id="uuid_b7460da0-42b2-4382-860d-a042b28382f8"/>zahlen. </p>
            <p xml:id="uuid_12fff93a-74a1-4658-adfe-deac1063624b" part="N"><lb xml:id="uuid_b6e47eac-bea6-46a3-a47e-acbea6e6a3e8"/>(gez.) Dr. <rs type="person" ref="#pmb57474">Püschel</rs> Dr. <rs type="person" ref="#pmb57476">Lampson</rs>
                <rs type="person" ref="#pmb57520">Wolff</rs>. </p>
            <p xml:id="uuid_145ed39f-0ef2-4eaf-b385-6d74b7617b64" part="N"><lb xml:id="uuid_050105a8-d4cd-4755-8105-a8d4cd87550c"/>[Unterschrift], <rs type="person" ref="#pmb57472">Justizangestellter</rs>, <lb xml:id="uuid_ae7e1fa1-4c78-4412-be1f-a14c78c41247"/>als Urkundsbeamter der
                Geschäftsstelle des <rs type="institution" ref="#pmb36834">Landgerichts III
                Berlin</rs>. </p>
            <p xml:id="uuid_f33aecc3-bf1d-42b4-b320-fba11de52b51" part="N"><lb xml:id="uuid_bc9bc0e2-5e50-46e4-9bc0-e25e5026e449"/>[Unterschrift] <lb xml:id="uuid_0e40debf-1e60-4aca-80de-bf1e601acac7"/>5. März 1931, <lb xml:id="uuid_e8e4a958-d9bf-4438-a4a9-58d9bfa438da"/>Justizinspektor, <lb xml:id="uuid_fecc4d25-bfca-4436-8c4d-25bfcaa43668"/><rs type="institution" ref="#pmb36834">III Berlin</rs>. <pb n="2" facs="#D_000146-021-000-facs001-l002-p002"/>
            </p>
